article_id:676,category_name:News,title_name:Another Daily Free Summon Event Incoming! [Update],image_path:,message:<div><span style="color: rgb(44, 130, 201);"><strong>Addendum <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1567231200"></span></strong></span></div><div>The Windswept Warriors summon showcase has been added to the applicable summon showcases!</div><div><br></div><div><span style="color: rgb(44, 130, 201);"><strong>Addendum <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1566885600"></span></strong></span></div><div>The Summon Showcase: Dragon Special has been added to the applicable summon showcases!</div><div><br></div><div>Another daily free summon event, which allows you to summon on the applicable summon showcases for free once per day, starts <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1566453600"></span>!</div><div><br></div><div>■Event Duration</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1566453600"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1567317540"></span></div><div><br></div><div>■Applicable Summon Showcases</div><div>You can summon on each of the following summon showcases for free once per day.</div><div><br></div><div>・A Crescendo of Courage</div><div>Note: You can summon up to one time during the one day from <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1566453600"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1566539940"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>・Ardent Admirers</div><div>Note: You can summon up to nine times during the nine days from <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1566453600"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1567231140"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>・Summon Showcase: Dragon Special</div><div>Note: You can summon up to four times during the four days from <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1566885600"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1567231140"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>・Windswept Warriors</div><div>Note: You can summon up to one time during the one day from <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1567231200"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1567317540"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>Notes:</div><div>1. You can summon for free on the applicable summon showcase once per day (each day is from 07:00 to 06:59 the next day).</div><div>2. The daily free summon resets each day at 07:00.</div><div>3. The Daily Deal, which allows you to summon once per day for 30 diamantium, can be used after performing your daily free summon.</div><div>4. For more information about summoning, tap Summon on the in-game footer menu, then select Showcase Info and check the Details tab.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1566367200,update_time1569478633